definitions.definition: A distinctive member ( Acinonyx jubatus ) of the cat family, slightly smaller than the leopard , but with proportionately longer limbs and a smaller head; native to Africa and southeast Asia (where it is nearly extinct) and also credited with being the fastest terrestrial animal.
